## Highlighting syntax for gherkin feature files
##
##"\|[[:space:]]*.*[[:space:]]*\|"

syntax "feature" "\.feature$"
icolor green "^[[:space:]]*(given|when|and|then).*\>"
icolor green start="\|" end="\|"
color brightgreen ""[^"]*""
color ,green "[[:space:]]+$"
color brightcyan "^@.*"
color brightblack "[[:space:]]*#.*\>"
color white "\|"
